5|$|The {{restaurant}} {{also sells}} takeaway cool boxes {{designed to be}} taken on flights to eat instead of airline food. There are up to four choices for each of three courses. Options include a tiger prawn and watercress salad, and roast beef <b>with</b> <b>truffle</b> <b>with</b> a green bean salad. Desserts include a chocolate and pecan brownie with crème Chantilly.|$|R
